ids-scaled-1.jpg 222w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/c5bf5/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 443w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/ff4da/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 886w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/82426/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 1329w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/60c6b/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 1772w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/bb9a8/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 886px) 100vw, 886px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 886px) 100vw, 886px\" srcset=\"/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/c7900/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 222w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/c5bf5/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 443w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/ff4da/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 886w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/82426/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 1329w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/60c6b/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 1772w,\n/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/bb9a8/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" src=\"/static/e5409781547f1c9045f9bb22d80f60d6/ff4da/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"2017 SA YES School Supply Distribution\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>It’s been a very busy few weeks for SA YES and the momentum isn’t slowing down.</h3>\n<p>Last week SA YES concluded their first ever Drive Away 4 Education Truck Raffle sponsored by <a href=\"https://www.ancira.com/\">Ancira Auto Group</a> and <a href=\"http://sbgi.net/\">Sinclair Broadcast Group</a>.  With over $113,000 raised in raffle ticket purchases, SA YES will be able to help 22,600 children in the San Antonio and surrounding areas.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nAnd what better time to see the results of SA YES’ efforts than during their annual school supply distribution as the children of San Antonio and Corpus Christi start a new school year.  In the last three weeks of August, SA YES will be visiting 48 schools within 5 school districts and distributing over 26,000 school supply kits by hand.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nSome of The PM Group staff have joined them by volunteering their time to pass out school supplies and even dress up in costumes to get the students excited for a new year of learning.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sayes.org\">If you want to find out more about SA YES’ incredible mission make sure to visit their website and learn more.</a><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\">About The PM Group</a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journal</em>. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"The PM Group Helps SA YES During School Supply Distribution","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"The PM Group Helps SA YES During School Supply Distribution","url":"/pm-group-helps-sa-yes-school-supply-distribution/"}],"title":"The PM Group & SA YES Distribute School Supplies to 48 Local Schools","metaDesc":"Some of The PM Group staff have joined them by volunteering their time to pass out school supplies to get the students excited for a new year of learning...","focuskw":"school","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"The PM Group & SA YES Distribute School Supplies to 48 Local Schools","opengraphDescription":"Some of The PM Group staff have joined them by volunteering their time to pass out school supplies to get the students excited for a new year of learning...","opengraphImage":{"altText":"2017 SA YES School Supply Distribution","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-square.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-square-300x300.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-square-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-square-150x150.jpg 150w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-square-768x768.jpg 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-square-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-square-2048x2048.jpg 2048w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/SA-YES-Distribution-Chase-and-Kids-square-1568x1567.jpg 1568w"},"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/pm-group-helps-sa-yes-school-supply-distribution/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u2019s Largest Advertising and Marketing Agency\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\"urlTemplate\":\"/?s={search_term_string}\"},\"query-input\":\"required name=search_term_string\"}],\"inLanguage\":\"en-